- () . (frequency response).

\(A_\text{}(w)=|H_\text{}(e^{i2\pi w})|\) , \(H_\text{}(z)=\sum_ih_iz^{-i}\) 

afc <- function(filter, omega) {
    k <- seq_along(filter) - 1
    h <- function(o) sum(rev(filter) * exp(-k*1i * o)) 
    abs(sapply(omega, h))
}

freq <- seq(0, pi, 0.001)
filt <- rep(1/12, 12)
omega <- freq/2/pi
plot(afc(filt, freq) ~ omega, type = "l", xaxt="n", main = "      = 12")
axis(1, at = c( 0, 1/12, 2/12, 3/12, 4/12, 5/12, 1/2), labels = c("0","1/12", "2/12", "3/12", "4/12", "5/12","1/2"), las = 2)
